Hi, i downloaded and installed Jamie Olivers 20 minute recipes, but it only plays the videos when connected to wifi or mobile data. It starts and asks if i want to download the videos now or later (both files are in on the phone). I click yes and it says the download is complete instantly, but if i hit skip it won't play videos even if i try to download them again unless i close the app. It isn't a big problem but is there a way to fix this. And thanks for all the apps, they all work perfectly, this is the only problem i have had with any of your apps.
